feat(auth)!: :sparkles: replace jwt lib

Why:
The jsonwebtoken library has known CVEs and lacks native TypeScript
types. jose is standards-compliant and provides full TS support with
zero native dependencies.

What:
Migrate all token signing from jwt.sign() to jose SignJWT builder
pattern. Verification now uses jwtVerify() with explicit algorithm
allowlist.

BREAKING CHANGE: JWT tokens signed with jsonwebtoken are incompatible
with jose. All active sessions will be invalidated. Users must log
in again after deployment.
